genresAdvancedInfo.name: tuna universitaria
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Tuna Universitaria is a lively and traditional music genre originating from Spanish and Portuguese universities. This genre features a group of university students who come together to perform with various instruments like guitars, mandolins, and tambourines. Tuna Universitaria is known for its cheerful melodies, harmonious vocals, and energetic performances.
